    "MissionGiver": "Crusader Industries",
    "Title": "RESOURCE DRIVE: SMALL CARGO SHIP RECOVERY",
    "TitleKey": "GoblinG_Crusader_RecoverCargo_S_Title",
    "Description": "A contractor of ours has abandoned their ship at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and we need someone to recover their cargo immediately.\n\nExpect to find between <EM4>50-55 SCU</EM4> of various box sizes, so a <EM4>standard multi-tool with a tractor beam attached </EM4> should suffice for moving everything to your hold. It\u2019s likely that there are still hostile forces in the area, but please recover as much of the cargo as possible, every contribution, great or small, matters. We\u2019ll pay you for as much as you can retrieve.\n\nOnce you\u2019ve found the cargo, safely transport it to a freight elevator at: <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address|ListAll)</EM4>. Our team will be sure to process it swiftly.\n\nIf you can find another pilot, it may be more convenient to fly the cargo ship directly, rather than having to transfer the cargo between ships. I\u2019ll leave the details to you.\n\nTake care.\n\n\nDenver Samuels\nContractor Liaison Officer\nCrusader Industries",
    "DescriptionKey": "GoblinG_Crusader_RecoverCargo_S_Desc",
    "DisplayDescription": "A contractor of ours has abandoned their ship at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> and we need someone to recover their cargo immediately.\n\nExpect to find between <EM4>50-55 SCU</EM4> of various box sizes, so a <EM4>standard multi-tool with a tractor beam attached </EM4> should suffice for moving everything to your hold. It\u2019s likely that there are still hostile forces in the area, but please recover as much of the cargo as possible, every contribution, great or small, matters. We\u2019ll pay you for as much as you can retrieve.\n\nOnce you\u2019ve found the cargo, safely transport it to a freight elevator at: <EM4>Orison</EM4>. Our team will be sure to process it swiftly.\n\nIf you can find another pilot, it may be more convenient to fly the cargo ship directly, rather than having to transfer the cargo between ships. I\u2019ll leave the details to you.\n\nTake care.\n\n\nDenver Samuels\nContractor Liaison Officer\nCrusader Industries",
